<h2 style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: #0e1629; line-height: 1.3;">
  Password changed successfully
</h2>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">
  Hello,
</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">
  This is a confirmation that the password for your HookStack account associated with <strong><%= @resource.email %></strong> has been changed.
</p>

<!-- Info box -->
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 24px 0;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 16px; background-color: #ecf1fd; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #2362ea;">
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.5;">
        <strong>Didn't change your password?</strong><br>
        If you didn't make this change, your account may have been compromised. Please reset your password immediately and contact our support team.
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.5;">
  This notification was sent for security purposes. No action is required if you made this change.
</p>
